OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUkraine war: Russian       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsoldier Vadim Shishimarin  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fjailed for life over war   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A court in Ukraine has jailed a Russian
OL,6, tank commander for life for killing a  
OL,7, civilian at the first war crimes trial 
OL,8, since the invasion.                    
OL,10,FCaptured soldier Sgt Vadim Shishimarin 
OL,11,Fwas convicted of killing Oleksandr     
OL,12,FShelipov, 62, in the north-eastern     
OL,13,Fvillage of Chupakhivka on 28 February. 
OL,15,FHe admitted shooting Mr Shelipov but   
OL,16,Fsaid he had been acting on orders and  
OL,17,Fasked forgiveness of the man's widow.  
OL,19,FMany other alleged war crimes are being
OL,20,Finvestigated by Ukraine.               
